examples.en: He has bought his uncle's business.
We used to dread my uncle's fortnightly visits.
She spent the summer doing manual labor on her uncle's farm.
I think my uncle's death was a merciful release for my poor aunt.
...could tolerate my uncle's foibles because we loved him dearly...
He changed his name to Lee in 1815 in compliance with his uncle's will.
His uncle's a car dealer and let him buy the car at cost (=without making a profit).
